<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC3">
<l>tiritantu ākilum tēvapirāṉ uṭaik</l>
<l>kariya kōlat tiruvuruk kāṇpaṉ nāṉ</l>
<l>periya vaṇkurukūr nakar nampikku āḷ</l>
<l>uriyaṉāy aṭiyēṉ peṟṟa naṉmaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though I wander aimlessly I see the</l>
<l>the dark form, the brilliant body of Tēvapirāṉ.</l>
<l>I, your slave, having become a worthy servant of</l>
<l>the Lord of the great, fertile Kurukūr city, is a great blessing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
